    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883000/extras/7a808f5fdef49249188bcd9463382ee0.poster.avif?t=1766565734\" width=1000 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883000/extras/7a808f5fdef49249188bcd9463382ee0.webm?t=1766565734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>伟大的皇帝某天突然驾崩—— <br>拥有继承权的是七位年轻的公主！<br>谁能从混乱当中拯救帝国！？<br>HEART of CROWN Online是以2022年重新制作的<br>「HEART of CROWN 2nd Edition」为原型的牌组建构式卡牌游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883000/extras/79e84a6ca45a36012351e90a65f76bbc.poster.avif?t=1766565734\" width=1000 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883000/extras/79e84a6ca45a36012351e90a65f76bbc.webm?t=1766565734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>这是一款回合制4人对战游戏。<br></li><li>请从自身领土获取资金，购买新的领土和效果丰富的行动卡，在战局中获取优势。<br></li><li>站稳脚跟后，就可以拥立公主了！每一位公主都拥有强大的能力，足以起到先发制人的效果。<br></li><li>将议员、公爵等权贵人士吸收到己方阵容，攒够20继承值即可举行加冕仪式，将王位据为己有。<br></li><li>游戏支持在线跨平台对战！也已搭载排名赛与自由对战模式。<br></li><li>即使是单人游玩，也能轻松享受丰富有趣的剧情模式。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883000/extras/edffc79e4b3c3a3c17487ba64c59da99.poster.avif?t=1766565734\" width=1000 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883000/extras/edffc79e4b3c3a3c17487ba64c59da99.webm?t=1766565734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>在世界仍被剑与魔法支配的豪迈时代，<br>存在一个达成统一大陆的伟业，给漫长的战乱画上句点的大帝国。<br>但眼看和平即将稳如磐石，伟大的皇帝却突然因病暴毙。<br>而且尚未来得及指定继位者…… <br>这样下去，世间搞不好会重燃战火！ <br><strong>身为帝国的权贵人士</strong>，<br>保证皇位免受撼动，让大陆获得安定的统一与和平是你的职责。<br>先帝并未诞下皇子，所幸留下了两名拥有直接血缘关系的公主。 <br>包括她们在内，<strong>备受拥戴的继承者共有七名</strong>。 <br>请选择一名想要拥立的公主，辅佐她登上皇位吧！",
